      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels that can still get the job done? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It has honest wear from age and use, but it still has plenty of life left for the right buyer. If you want something inexpensive with value and potential, this one is worth a look.",
