      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Honest budget-friendly driver with solid bones and plenty of usable life left. Starts, runs, and delivers the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it a great project, commuter, or weekend fixer-upper. Engine pulls through the rev range, transmission engages, and the chassis feels like a strong foundation for someone who appreciates a straightforward platform. Not perfect cosmetically and it shows its age, but it\u2019s an affordable way into dependable transportation with room to improve as you go.",
